data.text:
Michele Lee and Jason Reitman are divorced after a marriage of 9 years. They had 1 child.

They had a daughter named Josephine age 18.

About

Jason Reitman is a 46 year old Canadian Director. Born on 19th October, 1977 in Montreal, QC, Canada, he is famous for Son of Ivan Reitman, Thank You for Smoking in a career that spans 1998–present and 1988–present. His zodiac sign is Libra.
